node.text:
Ive been making music for like a year and some now and this is my first project I put out. At first I was nervous to hear the feedback because of the "comedy/music switch" comments. Over time I showed the the comedic side of me and the musical side of me can and will intertwine. Also I got AMAZING feedback from everyone about the project as a whole. I cant wait to share so so so much more with everyone. Always remember Love is stronger than Fear. If you wanna take a listen here's the link! https://song.link/album/us/i/1335102833 
Thank You!

user.full_name: J M O F I L M E D I T

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by (Angel)o on July 30, 2021 tagging @josselynmorris, and @listentoangelo. May be an image of 1 person, child, flower and outdoors.

node.text: I've had this account since 2012 always posting stuff i found funny and interesting, connecting with people all over the world at a young age. Sometimes it's hard to decipher what's really me and what's not. I appreciate a quiet life to myself and my studies but i also love the essence of community and making people happy. i notice i do that with just being around so there's a back and forth mental battle. But I always win when I wake up, feel the earth, look at people loving life, see others progressing to a better future, and when u get to eat food😂. Life keep going on, we can't stop the party 🫂💚

node.text: Me & @kennyjknox teamed up with a non profit organization called @todayimbrave to drop off masks at the wonderful @ruthelliscenter , a place in Detroit Michigan where the LGBTQ community can fully express themselves and get the help they need when it's not provided. This place felt like a really safe space with a bunch of lovely people😭 lmaoo bro me and kenny was chilling so hard they damn near kicked us out 💀blessed to bring awareness about a place like this. You can help other centers around the world when you simply buy a mask. 😁#icareaboutyou
